ily recommend columbia was this review … useful  funny  cool  gerry h naperville il  friends  reviews  photos share review embed review compliment send message follow gerry h stop following gerry h  listed in businesses that have no business being in business like several other notable formerly proud and once market leading companies see rayban hoover vacuum et alsorel has been purchased for its brand cache and is systematically being transformed into a made in china or viet nam fashion focused inferior product oriented over priced corporate cash cow  the heritage of quality and performance has been traded for return on investmentmy expensive sorels lasted exactly one hour in the subzero january temperatures that we have suffered recently in the midwest before they completely disintegrated  i returned them to the factory based on the instructions provided by the customer service person at sorel and the warranty evaluator rejected my claim  technically they were out of the warranty period but when you drop a buck fifty on a pair of winter boots you expect them to out perform your daughters hello kitty boots  that wasnt the case  if you want an exceptional pair of extreme weather boots grab a pair of us army surplus mickey mouse boots manufactured by bata  they are  absolutey the warmest most durable boots youll ever own and theyre available all over the internet for bout   skip the junk that columbia is cranking out in china and calling sorel was this review … useful  funny  cool  a a edmonton canada  friends  reviews share review embed review compliment send message follow a a stop following a a  i used to like columbia clothing as it was generally constructed of quality material the last two purchases have completely changed my mind i just spent  on a sweater that began to pill after just two washes the last sweater i bought turned into a giant ball of pilly fuzz within a week ill not spend another nickel on anything made by this brand was this review … useful  fun