 sunglasses impossible not to get a good deal back home i think they should hire a better stylist to put the clothes in a more attractive way and not so much as outlet display at least i like to buy things that are displayed in an attractive manner this store lacks the wow factor but still has everything i want every time i go and service has always been good no problem needed to return an online item and it was done with a smile i was on hold for  minutes trying to see if the columbia outlet near where i live would take it since i was returning sorel shoes i hung up because  minutes is too long to wait for an answer here they were pleasant took it and give me my money back its a large store with a big selection i would definitely come here to shop if i didnt have the friends and family discount which always makes it cheaper for me to shop online but i dont want to pay return shipping if it doesnt work out i have never been so upset with a company i live in the desert and i bought a coat to go to buffalo in january i purchased the coat on january  and paid extra for  day shipping it is now  days later and the coat has not arrived i was told by customer care that there was a snow storm that delayed my coat i was not informed of the delay and missed my chance to buy another coat i dont have enough balance on my card to purchase another coat and im cold awful they close at  and we were there  to pay for a jacket we decided and they didnt let us in bad customer service and not follow the operation time lazy employee employee norman has great customer service he honored and did a price adjustment since one of the jackets wasnt coming up  but there was a sign that said  off  didnt give me any hassle and was kind and friendly i had a horrible experience here when i tried to do an exchange last week there was one rude guy in the counter doing all the returnhe constantly kept complaining about customers trying to do return to the other guy in the counter infront of the other customers we went for an exchange  the guy turned us away after half hour wait even though we had all the receipts and tags keep off from this store and take your business elsewhere unless you like to be yelled at columbia sportswear unclaimed this business has not yet been claimed by the owner or a representative claim this business to view business statistics receive messages from prospective customers and respond to reviews  reviews details  opens a popup rating details  womens clothing mens clothing sports wear edit  opens a popup edit categories write a review add photo share  opens a popup bookmark  opens a popup get directions swap startend points start from start from swap startend points columbia sportswear  great mall dr milpitas ca  get directions edit  great mall drmilpitas ca  get directions phone number   business website columbiacom send to your phone shopping fashion womens clothing shopping fashion mens clothing shopping fashion sports wear shopping sporting goods sports wear sport polos by ray l womens section clothing by noelle y photo of columbia sportswear  milpitas ca united states by carmen v ad  day blinds shopathome services  reviews linda r said i dont often review experiences but had to post what a great great great experience we had with three day blinds we will for sure use them again we are pretty picky about work on the house and we… read more in shades  blinds home decor interior design ad suit  tux boutique  reviews  miles away from columbia sportswear al h said i usually dont write reviews on yelp but after reading a negative review about mikethe owner i deemed it necessary to write i have been to suit tux boutique multiple times for formal occasions as well… read more in formal wear mens clothing ask the community yelp users haven’t asked any questions yet about columbia sportswear ask a question recommended reviews for columbia sportswear your trust is our top concern so businesses cant pay to alter or remove their reviews learn 