y things that are displayed in an attractive manner this store lacks the wow factor but still has everything i want every time i go and service has always been good no problem needed to return an online item and it was done with a smile i was on hold for  minutes trying to see if the columbia outlet near where i live would take it since i was returning sorel shoes i hung up because  minutes is too long to wait for an answer here they were pleasant took it and give me my money back its a large store with a big selection i would definitely come here to shop if i didnt have the friends and family discount which always makes it cheaper for me to shop online but i dont want to pay return shipping if it doesnt work out employee norman has great customer service he honored and did a price adjustment since one of the jackets wasnt coming up  but there was a sign that said  off  didnt give me any hassle and was kind and friendly columbia sportswear unclaimed this business has not yet been claimed by the owner or a representative claim this business to view business statistics receive messages from prospective customers and respond to reviews  reviews details  opens a popup rating details  womens clothing mens clothing sports wear edit  opens a popup edit categories write a review add photo share  opens a popup bookmark  opens a popup get directions swap startend points start from start from swap startend points columbia sportswear  great mall dr milpitas ca  get directions edit  great mall drmilpitas ca  get directions phone number   business website columbiacom send to your phone shopping fashion womens clothing shopping fashion mens clothing shopping fashion sports wear shopping sporting goods sports wear sport polos by ray l womens section clothing by noelle y photo of columbia sportswear  milpitas ca united states by carmen v ad  day blinds shopathome services  reviews linda r said i dont often review experiences but had to post what a great great great experience we had