 hey lets check out those  off deals and surely there is always a shirt with the metallic inside that keep your super warm anywhereand that matches with the color of my sunglasses impossible not to get a good deal back home i think they should hire a better stylist to put the clothes in a more attractive way and not so much as outlet display at least i like to buy things that are displayed in an attractive manner this store lacks the wow factor but still has everything i want every time i go and service has always been good no problem needed to return an online item and it was done with a smile i was on hold for  minutes trying to see if the columbia outlet near where i live would take it since i was returning sorel shoes i hung up because  minutes is too long to wait for an answer here they were pleasant took it and give me my money back its a large store with a big selection i would definitely come here to shop if i didnt have the friends and family discount which always makes it cheaper for me to shop online but i dont want to pay return shipping if it doesnt work out i have never been so upset with a company i live in the desert and i bought a coat to go to buffalo in january i purchased the coat on january  and paid extra for  day shipping it is now  days later and the coat has not arrived i was told by customer care that there was a snow storm that delayed my coat i was not informed of the delay and missed my chance to buy another coat i dont have enough balance on my card to purchase another coat and im cold awful they close at  and we were there  to pay for a jacket we decided and they didnt let us in bad customer service and not follow the operation time lazy employee employee norman has great customer service he honored and did a price adjustment since one of the jackets wasnt coming up  but there was a sign that said  off  didnt give me any hassle and was kind and friendly i had a horrible experience here when i tried to do an exchange last week there was